# Request a Repair - Purple

A web service that allows users to report problems with their home.

## Getting started **with** Docker

```bash
docker-compose up
```

## Getting started **without** Docker

```bash
rails s
```

## Testing

### Start and stop the test server
```bash
bin/dtest-server up
bin/dtest-server down
```

Run Rake
```bash
bin/dspec
```

# Run specific tests
```bash
bin/dspec spec/features/*
```
### Or without Docker

```bash
bundle exec rspec spec
```

## Deploying

```bash
heroku buildpacks:set https://github.com/bundler/heroku-buildpack-bundler2
```

```bash
heroku create report-a-repair-purple --manifest --region eu
```
